/*EXI *  TEXT('Midas GL CS Fees Settlements Total Report')            *
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  Midas - General Ledger Module                                *
      *                                                               *
      *  GL1988 - Customer Service Fees Settlements Totals Report     *
      *                                                               *
      *  Function:  This program is a new report called to print      *
      *             details of fee settlements totals.                *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: GLC1988 - Customer Service Fees Settlements       *
      *             Total Control                                     *
