      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     FSDCURRL0IF  E           K        DISK         KINFSR *PSSR
      ** Currency file for ZCCYGB routine
      *
     FGLOTSTL3IF  E           K        DISK         KINFSR *PSSR
      ** Adjustment to Customer Service Fees - File
      *
     FGL1988AUO   E                    PRINTER      KINFSR *PSSR      UC
     F                                              KINFDS SPOOLU
      ** Adjustment to Customer Service Fees - Audit
      *
     FGL1988P1O   E                    PRINTER      KINFSR *PSSR      UC
     F                                              KINFDS SPOOL1
      ** Adjustment to Customer Service Fees - Report
      *
      /EJECT
      *
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  F U N C T I O N   O F   I N D I C A T O R S                  *
      *                                                               *
      *   01  - Total break will be performed                         *
      *   80  - Settlement Currency equal to 'blank'                  *
      *   89  - End of File                                           *
      *                                                               *
      *   98  - Date Format: DDMMYY (off); MMDDYY (on)                *
      * 90-99 - Used by Standard Subroutines                          *
      *                                                               *
      * U7+U8 - Database Error                                        *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      /SPACE 3
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  S U B R O U T I N E   I N D E X                              *
      *                                                               *
      *  SRBRCH - Subroutine to Retrieve Header description           *
      *  SRSVDA - Subroutine to Retrieve Sub-Header description       *
      *  SRACCR - Subroutine to Calculate Total                       *
      *  SRSETT - Subroutine to Calculate Subtotal                    *
      *  SRTRAI - Subroutine to write end of report and close file    *
      *  SRAUDT - Subroutine to Output Audit report                   *
      *  SRRCFP - Subroutine to register the P1 Printer File via RCF. *
      *  SRRCFA - Subroutine to register the AU Printer File via RCF. *
      *  *INZSR - Initial Processing                                  *
      *  *PSSR  - Error control subroutine                            *
      *  ZDATE2 - Convert Midas Day Number into Date (DDMMYY/MMDDYY)  *
      *  ZEDIT  - Insert a decimal point into a number and blank out  *
      *           leading zeroes                                      *
      *  ZCCYCN - Convert an amount in one currency to another        *
      *           currency using the spot rates for the two currencies*
      *  ZCCYGB - Convert an amount in one currency to an amount in   *
      *           another currency using the Swiss Konventionkurse    *
      *           exchange rates                                      *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     E                    CPY@    1   1 80
      ** Array containing Copyright statement
      *
     E/COPY ZSRSRC,ZDATE2Z1
     E/COPY ZSRSRC,ZPOWERZ1
     E/COPY ZSRSRC,ZEDITZ1
      *
      /SPACE 3
     ISPOOL1      DS
      ** File Information Data Structure for GL1988P1.
      *
     I                                       83  92 SFILE1
     I                                    B 123 1240SFNUM1
     I                                    B 188 1890OFLLN1
     I                                    B 367 3680PRTLN1
      *
     ISPOOLU      DS
      ** File Information Data Structure for SEU988AU.
      *
     I                                       83  92 SFILEU
     I                                    B 123 1240SFNUMU
      *
     IPSDS       SDS
      ** Program Status Data Structure
      *
     I                                     *PROGRAM PGM
     I                                      244 253 WSID
     I                                      254 263 USER
      *
     ILDA       E DSLDA                         256
      ** Local data area for database error details
      *
     ISDBANK    E DSSDBANKPD
      ** Bank Details
      *
     IDSFDY     E DSDSFDY
      ** Second DS For Access Programs, Short Data Structure
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                M A I N      P R O C E S S I N G               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** read file for record
      *
     C                     READ GLOTSTL3                 89
      *
      ** If End of Records, (*IN89), Perform: Audit Reporting (No
      ** Records).
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WWOPEN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN89     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C           PENT      IFEQ 'ALL'
     C           PENT      OREQ F7BRCA
      *
      ** Break update
      *
     C                     MOVE F7ACCY    RRACCY
     C                     MOVE F7STCY    RRSCCY
      *
     C           F7BRCA    IFNE RRBRCA
     C                     EXSR SRBRCH
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           F7BRCA    IFNE RRBRCA
     C           F7STVD    ORNE WWSTVD
     C                     EXSR SRSVDA
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Detail Cumulate Read Amount in Working Total Fields
      *
      ** Amount to settle in charging Ccy is :
      **    F7ACDT + F7MACP +/- F7OTAJ
      *
     C           F7ACDT    ADD  F7MACP    WKAMNT 150
     C           F7OTSG    IFEQ '+'
     C                     ADD  F7OTAJ    WKAMNT
     C                     ELSE
     C           F7OTSG    IFEQ '-'
     C                     SUB  F7OTAJ    WKAMNT
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ADD  WKAMNT    WWAMST
     C           F7AUID    IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     ADD  WKAMNT    WYAMST
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *
     C                     READ GLOTSTL3                 89
      *
      ** When break on Accrual Currency
      *
     C           F7BRCA    IFNE RRBRCA
     C           F7STVD    ORNE WWSTVD
     C           F7STCY    ORNE RRSCCY
     C           F7ACCY    ORNE RRACCY
     C           *IN89     OREQ *ON
     C           *IN01     IFEQ *ON
     C                     EXSR SRACCR
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** When break on Settlement Currency
      *
     C           F7BRCA    IFNE RRBRCA
     C           F7STVD    ORNE WWSTVD
     C           F7STCY    ORNE RRSCCY
     C           *IN89     OREQ *ON
     C           *IN01     IFEQ *ON
     C                     EXSR SRSETT
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *
      ** End of report
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON
     C           F7BRCA    ORNE RRBRCA
     C           *IN01     IFEQ *ON
     C                     EXSR SRTRAI
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           PENT      IFNE 'ALL'
     C           F7BRCA    ANDGTPENT
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN89
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WWOPEN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      ** When Break on Branch Code
      *
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRBRCH - Subroutine to Retrieve Header description           *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:                                                   *
      *  Calls: SRAUDT, SRRCFP                                        *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRBRCH    BEGSR
      *
     C           PENT      IFEQ 'ALL'
     C           PENT      OREQ F7BRCA
      *
     C           *IN01     IFEQ *ON
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     EXSR SRRCFP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRSVDA - Subroutine to Retrieve Sub-Header description       *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:                                                   *
      *  Calls: ZDATE2                                                *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRSVDA    BEGSR
      *
     C           WWOPEN    IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVE F7STVD    ZDAYNO
     C                     MOVE F7STVD    WWSTVD  50
     C                     EXSR ZDATE2
     C                     MOVE ZADATE    RRSTVD
     C                     MOVE F7BRCA    RRBRCA
      *
     C                     WRITEHEADP1
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN01
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRACCR - Subroutine to Calculate Total                       *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:                                                   *
      *  Calls: ZCCYGB, ZEDIT                                         *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRACCR    BEGSR
      *
     C           WWOPEN    IFEQ 'Y'
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         RQDLN1
     C           OFLLN1    SUB  PRTLN1    DIFLN1
     C           DIFLN1    IFLE RQDLN1
     C                     WRITEHEADP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** If Settlement currency isn't filled, then print only Charging amount
      *
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN80
     C           RRSCCY    IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN80
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE RRACCY    ZCCYF
     C                     MOVE RRSCCY    ZCCYT
      *
      ** Convert Charging Amount to Settlement and Cumulate
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWWAMST    ZAMTF
     C  N80                EXSR ZCCYGB
     C  N80                ADD  ZAMTT     WWTTAT
      *
      ** Edit WWAMST, ZCRSRT, ZAMTT
      *
     C                     Z-ADDZCDPF     ZADEC
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ZFIELD
     C                     MOVE ZAMTF     ZFIELD
     C                     EXSR ZEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZFIELD    RRTAMT
      *
     C           *IN80     IFEQ *ON
     C           'NO SETTL'CAT  '. A/C':0 RRFXRT    P
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   RRTSTT
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   RRSCCY
     C                     ELSE
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ZFIELD
     C                     MOVE ZCRSRT    ZFIELD
     C                     Z-ADD8         ZADEC
     C                     EXSR ZEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZFIELD    RRFXRT
      *
     C                     Z-ADDZCDPT     ZADEC
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ZFIELD
     C                     MOVE ZAMTT     ZFIELD
     C                     EXSR ZEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZFIELD    RRTSTT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Convert Charging Amount to Settlement Authorised and Cumulat  e
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWYAMST    ZAMTF
     C  N80                EXSR ZCCYGB
     C  N80                ADD  ZAMTT     WYTTAT
      *
      ** Edit WYAMST, ZCRSRT, ZAMTT
      *
     C                     Z-ADDZCDPF     ZADEC
     C                     MOVE ZAMTF     ZFIELD
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ZFIELD
     C                     EXSR ZEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZFIELD    RRAAMT
      *
     C           *IN80     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   RRASTT
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADDZCDPT     ZADEC
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ZFIELD
     C                     MOVE ZAMTT     ZFIELD
     C                     EXSR ZEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZFIELD    RRASTT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Reset Total amounts in Charging CCY
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     WWAMST
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     WYAMST
     C                     ADD  1         RCOUNT
      *
      ** Write Detail
      *
     C                     WRITEDETAIL
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRSETT - Subroutine to Calculate Subtotal                    *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:                                                   *
      *  Calls: ZEDIT                                                 *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRSETT    BEGSR
      *
     C           WWOPEN    IFEQ 'Y'
      *
     C                     Z-ADD3         RQDLN1
     C           OFLLN1    SUB  PRTLN1    DIFLN1
     C           DIFLN1    IFLE RQDLN1
     C                     WRITEHEADP1
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN80     IFEQ *OFF
      *
      *
     C                     MOVE RRSCCY    RRFCCY
      *
     C                     MOVE ZCDPT     ZADEC
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ZFIELD
     C                     MOVE WWTTAT    ZFIELD
     C                     EXSR ZEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZFIELD    RRTTAT
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ZFIELD
     C                     MOVE WYTTAT    ZFIELD
     C                     EXSR ZEDIT
     C                     MOVE ZFIELD    RRATAT
      *
      ** Reset Total amounts
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     WWTTAT
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     WYTTAT
      *
      ** Write TOTAL
      *
     C                     WRITETOTAL
      *
     C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITEBLKLIN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRTRAI - Subroutine to write end of report and close file    *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:                                                   *
      *  Calls:                                                       *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRTRAI    BEGSR
      *
     C           WWOPEN    IFEQ 'Y'
      *
      ** Check that sufficient lines remain for the Format. If not,
      ** write out the Main Headings on a new page.
      *
     C                     Z-ADD3         RQDLN1
     C           OFLLN1    SUB  PRTLN1    DIFLN1
     C           DIFLN1    IFLE RQDLN1
     C                     WRITEHEADP1
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     WRITETRAILP1
     C                     CLOSEGL1988P1
     C                     MOVE 'N'       WWOPEN
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRAUDT - Subroutine to Output Audit report                   *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: SRBRCH                                            *
      *  Calls: SRRCFA, *PSSR                                         *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRAUDT    BEGSR
      *
      ** Output Report Header and File Controls.
      *
     C           *INU7     IFEQ *ON
     C           RCOUNT    OREQ *ZERO
     C           WWOPEN    ANDEQ'Y'
     C                     EXSR SRRCFA
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** If there is a DB Error, Output the DB Error Information.
      *
     C           *INU7     IFEQ *ON
     C                     WRITEDBERROR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Or, if no records read, Output "No Details" message.
      *
     C           RCOUNT    IFEQ 0
     C           WWOPEN    ANDEQ'Y'
     C                     WRITENODTLS
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRRCFP - Subroutine to register the P1 Printer File via RCF. *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: SRBRCH                                            *
      *  Calls: ZSFILE                                                *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRRCFP    BEGSR
      *
      ** Open Report file
      *
     C                     OPEN GL1988P1
      *
      ** Ensure Report Spool File recorded by RCF.
      *
     C                     Z-ADDSFNUM1    PSNUM   60
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZSFILE'
     C                     PARM           PSEQ    5
     C                     PARM PENT      PENTY   3
     C                     PARM           SFILE1
     C                     PARM           PSNUM
     C                     PARM           PEROR   1
      *
      ** If Error occurs during ZSFILE processing, then return to the
      ** Calling Program.
      *
     C           PEROR     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INU7
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INU8
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WWOPEN  1
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRRCFA - Subroutine to register the AU Printer File via RCF. *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: SRAUDT                                            *
      *  Calls: ZSFILE                                                *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRRCFA    BEGSR
      *
      ** Ensure Audit Spool File recorded by RCF.
      *
     C                     OPEN GL1988AU
     C                     WRITEHEADAU
     C                     Z-ADDSFNUMU    PSNUMU  60
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZSFILE'
     C                     PARM           PSEQ
     C                     PARM PENT      PENTY
     C                     PARM           SFILEU
     C                     PARM           PSNUMU
     C                     PARM *BLANK    PEROR
      *
      ** If Error occurs during ZSFILE processing, then return to the
      ***  Calling Program.
      *
     C           PEROR     IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INU7
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INU8
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      /EJECT
      /TITLE  INITIAL PROCESSING
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *INZSR - Initial Processing                                  *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:                                                   *
      *  Calls: AOBANKR0, *PSSR                                       *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     C           *INZSR    BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PSEQ    5
     C                     PARM           PENT    3
      *
      ** Set up copyright parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           LDA
      *
      ** Access Bank details file
      *
     C                     CALL 'AOBANKR0'
     C                     PARM '       ' PRTCD   7
     C                     PARM '*FIRST ' POPTN   7
     C           SDBANK    PARM SDBANK    DSFDY
      *
     C           PRTCD     IFNE *BLANKS
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     Z-ADD1         DBASE
     C                     MOVEL'SDBANKPD'DBFILE    P
     C                     MOVEL'*FIRST'  DBKEY     P
     C                     MOVEL'GL1988'  DBPGM     P
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Set indicator 98 for date format used in ZDATE2
      *
     C           BJDFIN    IFEQ 'M'
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN98
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE BJCYCD    ZCCYB
      *
      ** Report Work fields.
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         RCOUNT  50
     C                     Z-ADD0         RQDLN1  30
     C                     Z-ADD0         DIFLN1  30
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   WWCCY   3
     C                     Z-ADD0         WWAMST 150
     C                     Z-ADD0         WYAMST 150
     C                     Z-ADD0         WWTTAT 150
     C                     Z-ADD0         WYTTAT 150
      *
     C                     MOVE 'N'       WWOPEN  1
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN80
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/*PSSR
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *PSSR  - Error control subroutine                            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: *INZSR                                            *
      *  Calls: SRAUDT                                                *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           *PSSR     BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INU7
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INU8
      *
      ** Check to see that *PSSR has not already been called.
      *
     C           WRUN      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WRUN    1
     C                     DUMP
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** If *PSSR already run, then just end the program here.
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      /EJECT
     C/COPY ZSRSRC,ZDATE2Z2
